{"name":"Running Throw","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>The hero knows how to use his momentum to boost the range of thrown weapons.</p>\n<p>If the character moves at least half his @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Movement]{Pace} immediately before making a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} roll to throw a weapon he increases the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Range]{Range} of his thrown weapon by 2/4/8. No other actions may be performed between moving and throwing, and the two maneuvers must be taken in the same round.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Bugbear, Half-orc, or Orc, Strength d8, Athletics d8"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_6tuhxfqx8df","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Racial Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"0OhD43FsghwLlX1g"}
{"name":"Guardian","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This character might be a professional bodyguard or just intensely devoted, but in either case he can jump in front of attacks intended for another. A character with this Edge must declare whom he is guarding at the beginning of any combat. As long as the guardian stays within 1\" of the chosen person, any attack aimed at that person is automatically rolled against the guardian instead. A guardian can switch charges during a battle, but doing so requires an action as the guardian re-focuses his attention.</p>\n<p>The character receives a benny each time he takes a Wound (not Shaken) while defending another character (Extra or Wild Card) during a specific encounter.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Slipstream Player's Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Fighting d6+, Notice d6+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_geq2hwpuzwp","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Professional Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"0sQSsFk8h7kQw3Cr"}
{"name":"Imbue Item","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Artificers in Eberron understand and can manipulate magical energy in such a way that enables them to quickly imbue items and constructs, including living constructs, with infusions (powers imbued on objects). This allows her to use any @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Powers]{power} normally available to Artificers of her @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Advancement]{Rank} or lower with a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Power Point]{Power Point} cost of 3 or lower and imbue any item with it.</p>\n<p>This takes one entire turn, during which she can do nothing else but make an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Arcane Backgrounds]{arcane skill} roll at an additional &ndash;2 to the Casting Modifier (she cannot take @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions] that turn).</p>\n<p>The artificer use of the device counts as a maintained power, but once its initial Duration is finished (it cannot be maintained) the item is not longer imbued.</p>\n<p><em>Renaming and modification of the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Gadgeteer]{Gadgeteer} edge.</em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Modified from Savage Worlds Adventure Edition</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Dragonmark of Making or Magecraft), arcane skill d6+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_kir10d62ppq","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Power Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"1Lgpii25virOuiKE"}
