{"name":"Bilge Rat","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Scuttling around in the bowels of the ship doesn&rsquo;t suit every sailor, but this character has learned to adjust to the cramped conditions below deck.</p>\n<p>The character no longer suffers the &ndash;2 penalty when fighting below decks or in small quarters. If the weapon has a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Reach]{Reach}&nbsp;value the &ndash;2 penalty applies as normal.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Fighting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_1jrlkylls1t","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"HxXbXHQgeCRaEkes"}
{"name":"Fanaticism","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This Edge is most appropriate for members of the military, but the leader of a seasoned band of monster hunters might develop it as well.</p>\n<p>Troops under command of a character with this Edge add +2 to their @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fear]{Fear} checks and subtract 2 from rolls on the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-tables.Fear Table]{Fear Table}.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: Hellfrost Player Guide</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fervor"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_n7sal0llwjb","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Leadership Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"IleV3zVw636yA8NN"}
