{"name":"Storm Chaser","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>When the weather is at its worst the character is at his best, seeming to read the storm like he would a book. Such characters are respected for their skill but feared for their love of a good storm.</p>\n<p>The character receives +1 to all @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Piloting]{Piloting} rolls made during a storm. In addition, the character may draw two cards during a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Chases and Vehicles]{Chases} each round during a storm and keep the best card, as long as he is the Captain. If the character has the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Wind Sense]{Wind Sense} Edge as well he draws three cards.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Boating or Piloting d8+"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_uyw9lec3zf8","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Weird Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"yxDVywPQB9wdev5s"}
{"name":"Improved Bilge Rat","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"type":"edge","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>Scuttling around in the bowels of the ship doesn&rsquo;t suit every sailor, but this character has learned to adjust to the cramped conditions below deck.</p>\n<p>The character can use any weapon below decks without incurring the &ndash;2 penalty for fighting in cramped conditions.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Source: 50 Fathoms</strong></em></p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Bilge Rat"}},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_1jrlkylls1t","path":"Edges#/CF_SEP/Combat Edges","color":"#000000"}},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","effects":[],"_id":"zELwajT1ypnZJM19"}
